author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Saigon Soul Revival performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 7, 2024. 

Songs:
Ai Thật Lòng Yêu Ai 00:00
Mơ Xuân 04:00
Đám Cưới Nhà Em 07:38
Nào Ta Cùng Hát 11:12
Sầu Đông 15:09

Minh Anh Nguyễns - Vocals
Đăng Nguyễn Khoa - Keyboards
Indy Laville - Guitar & Đàn Nguyệt
Gabriel Kaouro - Bass
Hiếu Nguyễn Hương Bảo - Drums
Hải Phượng Nguyễn - Đàn Tranh & Đàn Bầu

Audio & Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz
Audio Mixer: Julian Martlew
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Carlos Cruz
